metadata.name: MoneyBall #1
metadata.description: MoneyBall NFTs Is a project targeted towards new investors/entrepreneurs looking to get into the NFT space. We are  looking to create a safe trustworthy project and good community; not only to make you money but to help you learn and grow while surrounding yourself with like minded people. There will be multiple giveaways to NFT owners with chances of 1 on 1 Mentorship and much much more!
